<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Postmaster on BenzHub</title><link>https://benzhub.github.io/tags/postmaster/</link><description>Recent content in Postmaster on BenzHub</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-TW</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://benzhub.github.io/tags/postmaster/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>背景進程：PostgreSQL 的幕後工作者們 | PostgreSQL</title><link>https://benzhub.github.io/post/postgresql/011-background-processes/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://benzhub.github.io/post/postgresql/011-background-processes/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PostgreSQL&lt;/strong&gt; 是多進程架構，除了處理客戶端請求的 Backend Process，還有一批背景進程（Background Processes）負責維護資料庫的健康。理解 &lt;strong&gt;Postmaster&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;Checkpointer&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;Background Writer&lt;/strong&gt;、&lt;strong&gt;Autovacuum&lt;/strong&gt; 等進程的職責、觸發條件與調校參數，是效能調校與穩定性維護的核心知識。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>